THIS IS THE CHANGELOG OF THE "Rchoice" PACKAGE

      CHANGES IN VERSION 0.2  (2014-12-16)

* added a new function to compute the standard error of the variance-covariance matrix of random parameters

* more flexibility to model hirarchical variables

* added the Johnson's Sb function

* added the rFormula and related functions

* models allow panel data models

* added new function to get the conditional mean of the random parameters for each individual

* initial values for standard deviation of random parameters are set to 0.1. Previously was 0

* slightly improved documentation